      the client used to execute a CommandRequest which belongs to PowserShell and also can be single instated to handle PowserShell command
      class  RestfClient
      the client used to execute a RestfRequest and also can be single instated to handle Restf web service Request Some properites like proxy you can configured in the file which path is "%userprofile%\.rest-client\rest-client.properties", that file will be generated after you executed a request on time.
      class  ScenarioClient

      class  SQLClient
      the client used to execute a CommandRequest which belongs to oracle's SQL and also can be single instated to handle oracle's SQL
      class  SSHClient
